Project name : Peddy

Short description : this side is make for pet lovers . in this side you can adopt an pet . you will able to like or add to card an pet for adopting and you also do to check each pets details 5 key features :

1 . responsive

2 . each pet categories function

3 . each pet details

4 . sort function

5 . adopt modal , like function , API

ES6 features used. : arrow function , Distracting

